{"tid":544028,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【發哥發火】周潤發入稟高院　要求製片商就《賭城風雲》賠償","createTime":"2018-01-29T06:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T02:38:33.000Z","uid":39464,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"286311138096a11210f1d6a1fe0cdd70876cdd56","tid":544028,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T06:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180129/s00001/811cd798ff3e08f34aaf0e178b568f5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180129%2Fs00001%2F811cd798ff3e08f34aaf0e178b568f5d.jpg&h=b4e2bb6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主演電影《賭城風雲》1至3集的著名演員周潤發，日前經其出任董事的公司入稟高等法院，指電影製片商博納影視娛樂有限公司違約，要求博納支付相關費用，及交出合約文件等，並就違約問題作出賠償，惟原訴未有在入稟狀透露合約金額。<br />\n<br />\n原訴為周潤發夫婦出任董事的藝才製作有限公司，及Misto Trading Limited；被告為製片人于冬創辦的博納影視娛樂有限公司。<br />\n<br />\n原訴於入稟狀要求法庭頒令要被告交出2013年至2015年，原訴與被告就電影《賭城風雲》1至3集簽下合約的文件、未支付款項及相關利息，並就被告違約作出賠償。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180129/s00001/1517199077403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180129%2Fs00001%2F1517199077403&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCxwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=16d26e47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180129%2Fs00001%2F1517199077403&h=a86ec51d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180129/s00001/1517199077403</a>"},{"pid":"209c2dde732ee18053a2eeb1afd0a9b84c4f19c5","tid":544028,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T06:18:17.000Z","msg":"香港法院告到大陸公司咩?"},{"pid":"2fbe6025b3c2c9ada15b40009aab47a495c11029","tid":544028,"uid":103207,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T06:19:41.000Z","msg":"好似話份約係跟票房分紅,<br />\n<br />\n有人吹到套戲30億票房<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0977e